        "content": "### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: domestic, international + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'domestic' → Google Sheets · ②→ Fast-Track 'international' + Alert · ③→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)",
